Class BackendDeploymentPlan

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.kinst.jakub.diploma.offloading.model.BackendDeploymentPlan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class BackendDeploymentPlan
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class representing a plan of backend deployment. It basically stores which IP address should be used for each backend ID. This is a product of the Planner component.

    --------------------------- Created by Jakub Kinst 2015 E-mail: jakub@kinst.cz
